t the time i just look to try new things (which rarely gets done if it's not solo'able). Really i find elitist attitudes hilarious, because it's that narrow sightedness that turns eq into more of a job than a game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
